{"tid":1683430,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港式抗爭] 黃色經濟圈背後真正信念","createTime":"2019-10-30T15:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T07:02:45.000Z","uid":29381,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6aca23afcd8573417ab28bb9c1bca56fa27e105e","tid":1683430,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:40:47.000Z","msg":"好多人覺得黃色經濟圈單純係趕絕藍餐廳同埋補償黃餐廳 <br />\n但我想話你知唔係咁簡單 希望大家抽少少時間思考下<br />\n<br />\n1. 睇到團結既威力 提高身份認同感同埋動員力<br />\n2. 令商戶明白如果你想做香港人生意 就要撐香港人 <br />\n3. 黃色經濟圈形成後香港人就會有同政府談判既力量  <br />\n4. 將政治帶入生活 謝絕政治潔癖  <br />\n5. 抹走白色恐怖 政治打壓<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係咩? 黃色經濟圈岩晒和理非同埋現時環境<br />\n希望大家僅記背後信念 一生實踐黃色經濟圈 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687ed33bc996296c769c9bc0b2563827fe83fb27","tid":1683430,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24aa1b5b6f3d7562933c1f46c20d722102bae9f3","tid":1683430,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:02:30.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"bb49d71fe6c49fdde1e9367645a31871db8707d5","tid":1683430,"uid":35063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:26:33.000Z","msg":"樓豬帶我食好西未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bcbd2453940dc5f84da0058867a9c4a36359a0d","tid":1683430,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係講笑,加藤屋啲嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as